  <artifactId>nuxeo-platform-syndication</artifactId>
  <name>*DEPRECATED* Nuxeo Syndication Service</name>
  <description>
    Nuxeo Enterprise Platform: Syndication Service. This service build
    syndication feeds (RSS &amp; ATOM) on content objects. It defines Interfaces
    so that any content object implementing those interfaces can produce
    syndication feeds or be included in it. As of Nuxeo 5.4.2, it is deprecated
    since content views already offer RSS and ATOM exports.
  </description>

